Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===AVANT===
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花为了什么而开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了让大家幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了大家的笑脸 花儿才会这般绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.38,0:01:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你永恒的治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===OP===
